room_title: Escape room "Dark Sector" by Planet Deadline Escape Rooms in Colorado Springs
room_description: You're a research team working at a classified government facility on the moon called Area 53. One day, the experiment gets out of control and the lab goes on lockdown. With a mutant monster now ravaging free in the halls of the lab, your lives are in great danger! Will you find a way to return to planet Earth before getting blown up into space or being eaten alive?
